data.description: This is an amazing solar home with multiple Tesla batteries. Live the vacation lifestyle in this fabulous 5 plus bedroom and 4.5 bath home. An immaculate well-planned 4004 soft floorpan. Entertainer's delight with a gourmet kitchen, breakfast bar and nook. This home includes a spacious master suite with sitting area, fireplace and balcony with views to downtown and Coronado Bridge. The inviting backyard include a pool, spa, pool house with bar, BBQ and full bath. This home also includes a putting green and children's play area. An abundance of indoor and outdoor space. Minutes away from schools, shopping and restaurants.Panoramic views of ocean, mountains, downtown and Coronado Bridge from this magnificent home with paid solar. Prime location on cul-de-sac. Refreshing pool and spa adjacent to pool house with bar, grill and full bath. Pristine putting green and children's play area. An abundance of indoor and outdoor space. Luxury inside and out. An entertainer's dream! Tile and wood flooring throughout. Elegant master suite with balcony. Immaculate gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry and plenty of beautifully designed cabinets for storage. Spacious family room. Upstairs office with lots of light and majestic view. Storage areas behind pool house, children's play area, attic and garage. Extra room downstairs may be used as bedroom, office or children's study area. Minutes away from shopping and restaurants.
